title: #66 - Hotline Edition: How Do You Find Someone That Can Fly Me in a Private Jet?
description:
It’s another Hotline Edition of the podcast! If YOU would like to ask Maria a question on an upcoming episode, make sure to follow her on Instagram to know when the hotline will be open next! Follow her at @matchmakermaria 

This week… 

How do you find someone that can fly me in a private jet? 

How to ask a potential partner their relationship history?

What do you do when you enjoy spending time with someone, but you’re not sure you want to keep dating?

Follow Maria on Instagram at http://instagram.com/matchmakermaria 

If you’d like to learn more about Agape Match’s services or enroll in an upcoming Agape Intensive, visit agapematch.com/services
